      <div class="gem-c-title
  
  gem-c-title--margin-bottom-5">
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text ">
    Media enquiries
  </h1>
</div>

    </div>
    
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    HM Revenue & Customs’ (HMRC) press office deals with all areas of the department’s work and all media, including national, regional, trade, print, broadcast and web. 
  </p>

      
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-row ">
