  <li>Capital Gains Tax</li>
  <li>Inheritance Tax</li>
  <li>Savings & Investments</li>
  <li>Stamp Duty Land Tax</li>
  <li>High Net Worth Unit</li>
  <li>Affluent Unit</li>
  <li>Residency issues</li>
  <li>Offshore taxation</li>
  <li>Pensions</li>
