<h2 id="out-of-hours">Out of hours</h2>

<p>Tel: 07860 359 544</p>

<p>This is the single contact number for all emergency out-of-hours national and regional media enquiries, which operates outside normal office hours (9.00 am to 6.00 pm, Monday to Friday).</p>

